# Privacy Policy for CreatorBio AI

Last updated: January 28, 2026

CreatorBio AI respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our mobile application.

## 1. Information We Collect

We may collect the following types of information:

- Personal Information: Name, email address (only if you contact support)
- App Usage Data: App interactions, feature usage, crash reports
- Device Information: Device model, operating system version
- Network Information: IP address (for analytics and security purposes)

We do NOT collect:
- Precise location
- Contacts
- Messages
- Photos or videos without your permission
- Sensitive personal data

## 2. How We Use Your Information

We use the collected data to:
- Improve app performance
- Fix bugs and crashes
- Provide AI-generated bios and content
- Enhance user experience
- Respond to support queries

## 3. Third-Party Services

CreatorBio AI may use trusted third-party services:

- Firebase Analytics
- Firebase Crashlytics
- AI API providers (for generating bios and content)

These services follow their own privacy policies and comply with data protection standards.

## 4. Data Security

We use industry-standard security practices to protect your data. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure.

